					<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content"><div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">2020 series of riots in Delhi, India</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">


</p>
<table class="infobox vevent" style="width:25.5em;border-spacing: 2px;"><tbody><tr><th colspan="2" class="infobox-above summary" style="background-color:#CEE0F2;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;">2020 Delhi riots</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-image" style="text-align: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><div style="background-color:#000000;border-collapse:collapse;border:0px solid black;width:300px;display:table;margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"><div style="display:table-row"><div style="display:table-cell;border-top:0;padding:2px 0 0 2px"><div style="display:table;background-color:#000000;border-collapse:collapse"><div style="display:table-row"><div style="display:table-cell;border-top:0;padding:0 2px 2px 0"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:North_East_Delhi_Riots_2020_(1).jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ed/North_East_Delhi_Riots_2020_%281%29.jpg/300px-North_East_Delhi_Riots_2020_%281%29.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="225" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ed/North_East_Delhi_Riots_2020_%281%29.jpg/450px-North_East_Delhi_Riots_2020_%281%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ed/North_East_Delhi_Riots_2020_%281%29.jpg/600px-North_East_Delhi_Riots_2020_%281%29.jpg 2x" data-file-width="4160" data-file-height="3120" /></a></span></div></div></div><div style="display:table;background-color:#000000;border-collapse:collapse"><div style="display:table-row"><div style="display:table-cell;border-top:0;padding:0 2px 2px 0"><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Relief_camps_for_Delhi_riot-affected_victims.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Relief_camps_for_Delhi_riot-affected_victims.jpg/300px-Relief_camps_for_Delhi_riot-affected_victims.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="225" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Relief_camps_for_Delhi_riot-affected_victims.jpg/450px-Relief_camps_for_Delhi_riot-affected_victims.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Relief_camps_for_Delhi_riot-affected_victims.jpg/600px-Relief_camps_for_Delhi_riot-affected_victims.jpg 2x" data-file-width="4160" data-file-height="3120" /></a></span></div></div></div></div></div></div>
<div style="font-size:95%">(top) Muslim homes and businesses were set on fire during the rioting in <span class="nowrap">Shiv Vihar, Delhi</span>.<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2">&#91;a&#93;</a></sup><br /> (bottom) A relief camp at <a href="/wiki/Eidgah" title="Eidgah">Eidgah</a> in <a href="/wiki/Mustafabad,_Delhi" title="Mustafabad, Delhi">Mustafabad, Delhi</a> set up by the <a href="/wiki/Government_of_Delhi" title="Government of Delhi">Government of Delhi</a><sup id="cite_ref-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-3">&#91;b&#93;</a></sup> and the Muslim <a href="/wiki/Waqf" title="Waqf">Waqf</a> board, with beds for 800 women and 700 men, and with doctors from <a href="/wiki/St_Stephen%27s_Hospital,_Delhi" title="St Stephen&#39;s Hospital, Delhi">St Stephens Hospital</a> and <a href="/w/index.php?title=Holy_Family_Hospital_(New_Delhi)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Holy Family Hospital (New Delhi) (page does not exist)">Holy Family Hospital</a> volunteering.<sup id="cite_ref-5" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-5">&#91;c&#93;</a></sup></div></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Date</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;">23 February 2020 – 29 February 2020 (6&#160;days)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Location</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;"><div style="display:inline;" class="location"><a href="/wiki/North_East_Delhi" class="mw-redirect" title="North East Delhi">North East Delhi</a>, India</div><br /><span class="geo-inline"><span class="plainlinks nourlexpansion load-gadget" data-gadget="WikiMiniAtlas"><a class="external text" href="https://geohack.toolforge.org/geohack.php?pagename=2020_Delhi_riots&amp;params=28.682_N_77.274_E_region:IN_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki"><span class="geo-nondefault"><span class="geo-dms" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location"><span class="latitude">28°40′55″N</span> <span class="longitude">77°16′26″E</span></span></span><span class="geo-multi-punct">&#xfeff; / &#xfeff;</span><span class="geo-default"><span class="geo-dec" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location">28.682°N 77.274°E</span><span style="display:none">&#xfeff; / <span class="geo">28.682; 77.274</span></span></span></a></span></span></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Caused by</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Hate_speech" title="Hate speech">Hate speech</a><sup id="cite_ref-IT2_6-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IT2-6">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Provocation_(legal)" class="mw-redirect" title="Provocation (legal)">Provocation</a><sup id="cite_ref-Mishra_DNA_2_7-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Mishra_DNA_2-7">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Confrontation" title="Confrontation">Confrontation</a><sup id="cite_ref-Mishra_DNA_2_7-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Mishra_DNA_2-7">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/CAA_Protests" class="mw-redirect" title="CAA Protests">CAA Protests</a><sup id="cite_ref-8" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-8">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Mass_mobilization#Mass_mobilization_in_social_media" title="Mass mobilization">Mass mobilization</a><sup id="cite_ref-NDTV1_9-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-NDTV1-9">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Religious_nationalism" title="Religious nationalism">Religious nationalism</a><sup id="cite_ref-IT2_6-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IT2-6">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-Mosque_burnt_10-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Mosque_burnt-10">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>
</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Goals</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;">
<ul><li>Preventing <a href="/wiki/Citizenship_Amendment_Act_protests" title="Citizenship Amendment Act protests">Citizenship Amendment Act protests</a><sup id="cite_ref-Mishra_DNA_2_7-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Mishra_DNA_2-7">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-NDTV1_9-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-NDTV1-9">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Ethnic_persecution" class="mw-redirect" title="Ethnic persecution">Ethnic</a> and <a href="/wiki/Religious_persecution" title="Religious persecution">religious persecution</a><sup id="cite_ref-11" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-11">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li>Clearing roads blocked by protestors<sup id="cite_ref-:0_12-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-:0-12">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>
</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Methods</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;"><ul class="cslist"><li><a href="/wiki/Riot" title="Riot">Rioting</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Arson" title="Arson">arson</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Burglary" title="Burglary">burglary</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Shooting" title="Shooting">shooting</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" class="infobox-header" style="background-color:#CEE0F2;">Casualties</th></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Death(s)</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;">53<sup id="cite_ref-thewire-2020-2-12_13-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-thewire-2020-2-12-13">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>
<ul><li>2 unidentified<sup id="cite_ref-thewire-2020-2-12_13-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-thewire-2020-2-12-13">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li>36 Muslims<sup id="cite_ref-thewire-2020-2-12_13-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-thewire-2020-2-12-13">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li>15 Hindus<sup id="cite_ref-thewire-2020-2-12_13-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-thewire-2020-2-12-13">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>
</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Injuries</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;">200+<sup id="cite_ref-14" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-14">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label" style="white-space:nowrap;padding-right:0.65em;">Arrested</th><td class="infobox-data" style="line-height:1.3em;">2200 (including detained)<sup id="cite_ref-IT690Cases_15-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-IT690Cases-15">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="infobox-below" style="border-top:1px #aaa solid"><div class="mw-kartographer-container thumb tnone center"><div class="thumbinner" style="width: 300px;"><a class="mw-kartographer-map notheme" style="width: 300px; height: 227px;" data-mw-kartographer="mapframe" data-style="osm-intl" data-width="300" data-height="227" data-zoom="11" data-lat="28.676792" data-lon="77.273456" data-overlays="[&quot;_588a9793889afe2762665135a58a3299389e5b33&quot;]" href="/wiki/Special:Map/11/28.676792/77.273456/en"><img src="https://maps.wikimedia.org/img/osm-intl,11,28.676792,77.273456,300x227.png?lang=en&amp;domain=en.wikipedia.org&amp;title=2020+Delhi+riots&amp;revid=1220974845&amp;groups=_588a9793889afe2762665135a58a3299389e5b33" width="300" height="227" decoding="async" srcset="https://maps.wikimedia.org/img/osm-intl,11,28.676792,77.273456,300x227@2x.png?lang=en&amp;domain=en.wikipedia.org&amp;title=2020+Delhi+riots&amp;revid=1220974845&amp;groups=_588a9793889afe2762665135a58a3299389e5b33 2x" alt="Map" /></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
<table class="sidebar nomobile nowraplinks"><tbody><tr><td class="sidebar-pretitle" style="padding-bottom:0.25em;">Part of <a href="/wiki/Category:Anti-Muslim_violence_in_India" title="Category:Anti-Muslim violence in India">a series</a> on</td></tr><tr><th class="sidebar-title-with-pretitle" style="background:#41924B;padding:0.25em;border-bottom:5px solid whitesmoke;"><a href="/wiki/Violence_against_Muslims_in_independent_India" title="Violence against Muslims in independent India"><span class="tmp-color" style="color:white">Violence against Muslims<br />in independent India</span></a></th></tr><tr><th class="sidebar-heading" style="background:#41924B;padding-bottom:0.15em;color:white;">
Major incidents</th></tr><tr><td class="sidebar-content plainlist" style="padding-top:0.2em;">
<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Hyderabad_massacres" title="Hyderabad massacres">1948 Hyderabad massacres</a></li>
