<li id="cite_note-36"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-36">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFKuchay2020" class="citation news cs1">Kuchay, Bilal (24 February 2020). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/02/fresh-violence-erupts-indian-capital-anti-caa-protests-200224121139653.html">"Fresh violence erupts in Indian capital during anti-CAA protests"</a>. <i>Al Jazeera</i><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">25 May</span> 2020</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Al+Jazeera&amp;rft.atitle=Fresh+violence+erupts+in+Indian+capital+during+anti-CAA+protests&amp;rft.date=2020-02-24&amp;rft.aulast=Kuchay&amp;rft.aufirst=Bilal&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2020%2F02%2Ffresh-violence-erupts-indian-capital-anti-caa-protests-200224121139653.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3A2020+Delhi+riots" class="Z3988"></span></span>
